sect1.para:
Setting up your database to use Veil2 is a
fairly straightforward process, and can be done in the following
stages:

  install the Veil2 scripts;
  choose and implement your authentication mechanisms;
  choose and implement your authentication mechanisms;
  identify and define your security contexts;
  create an initial set of privileges and roles;
  create foreign key links for
  veil2.accessors;
  create links for security contexts;
  create scope promotion mechanisms;
  secure your tables;
  secure your views;
  assign initial roles to users;
  test
